Project Proposal:

Stack:
I'll be using React for the front-end and Node.js for the back-end. I'll also be using PostgreSQL for my database.

Focus:
The focus of this application will be evenly spread between front and back end development.

Type:
The app will be a website

Goal:
The goal is to help pet owners track the health of their pets. And have a centralized place to do it all.

Data:
The app will use a custom-build api with data such as:

user profiles consiting of names, emails, phone numbers and pet profiles consisting of age species name.
